                            <i class="fas fa-quote-right "></i>
                        </div>

                        <p style="color:black; padding-top:5%; text-align: justify; font-size:medium">"At dreamy, we believe that every piece of furniture is a step towards building a home filled with warmth and inspiration. Remember, the spaces we create today shape the dreams we achieve tomorrow."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-5">
                    <div class="bg-white py-5 px-4" style="border-radius:20px; box-shadow: 6px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);">
                        <img src="~/images/man4.jpg" alt="" width="100" class="img-fluid rounded-circle mb-3 img-thumbnail shadow-sm">
