                        <div class="quote-icon" style="font-size: 50px; color: grey; padding-top: 5%;">
                            <i class="fas fa-quote-right "></i>
                        </div>

                        <p style="color:black; padding-top:5%; text-align: justify; font-size:medium">"Inspiration is the fuel for innovation. Let your passion be the driving force that turns those dreams into reality. We believe that everything starts with a dream. Together, we can create spaces that inspire and uplift every day."</p>

